--- !u!1001 &747982202
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Queen: States if they are next to at least one ghost. Could be one
        ghost and one subject, or two subjects


        Manservant: States a character
        is a subject. Will always select ghosts if lying, or subjects if telling
        the truth


        Bard: States how far away they are from the closest ghost.
        If lying, states how far away they are from the closest subject


        Nun:
        States two potential subjects the ghost could be. One or both of the subjects
        could be ghosts. If lying, neither will be ghosts


        Knight: the second
        character is a ghost if and only if the first is a subject. If lying, the
        second character is a subject'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 649765280201625091, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Butler: States a character is lying. Will always select ghosts if lying,
        or ghosts if telling the truth


        Doctor: States an honest subject,
        lying subject and a ghost. If lying, will call a ghost a lying subject and
        a lying subject a ghost


        Alchemist: States if they are next to at
        least one lying subject. Could be one ghost and one subject, or two subjects


        Troubadour:
        States two potential subjects that could be lying. One or both of the subjects
        could be lying. If lying, will choose one more more ghosts, and will never
        pick lying subjects


        ALL GHOSTS: Disguises as a random subject and
        gives false information


        Phantom: A subject next to me lies


        Nuckelavee:
        Subjects next to me lie'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7178253644178797337, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_PresetInfoIsWorld
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
